---
import Layout from '../app/components/layout.astro'
import Listing from '../modules/articles/components/listing.svelte'
---

<Layout title="Articles" path="/articles">
  <section>
    <h1 class="text-xl">
      I usually love to share many stories from programming, and games to
      lifestyles on my blog. Here're the latest blogs that I wrote. If you want
      to learn more about articles that I wrote, please have a look at <a
        href="https://blog.rayriffy.com">Riffy Blog</a
      >.
    </h1>
  </section>

  <section
    class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 items-center"
  >
    <Listing client:load />
  </section>
</Layout>
